OL,3,CPetition to save popular beach cafe
OL,4,Creceives nearly 3,000 signatures
OL,6,FMore than 2,700 people have signed a
OL,7,Fpetition to save the popular Fermain
OL,8,FBeach Cafe in .
OL,10,FBelmiro and Manuela de Frietas have
OL,11,Frun it for 21 years but are facing an
OL,12,Funcertain future with their lease on
OL,13,Fthe government-owned site due to
OL,14,Fexpire on 31 October.
OL,16,FA tender process is underway which
OL,17,Fwill close on Friday 17 May, with
OL,18,Fother interested parties bidding to
OL,19,Ftake over the site.
